Pernambuco Championship 1930

Source: "Campeonato Pernambucano - 1915 a 1970", book written by 
Carlos Celso Cordeiro and Luciano Guedes Cordeiro.
20/04/30     Encruzilhada 3-1 Torre
20/04/30     Santa Cruz 1-1 Íris-PE
20/04/30     Sport Recife 0-2 Náutico
27/04/30     América-PE 2-0 Flamengo (RE)
27/04/30     Náutico 4-1 Encruzilhada
04/05/30     América-PE 5-3 Íris-PE
04/05/30     Torre 2-1 Santa Cruz
11/05/30     Encruzilhada 2-0 Sport Recife
11/05/30     Náutico 2-3 Torre
11/05/30     Santa Cruz 1-1 América-PE
18/05/30     Íris-PE 1-3 Flamengo (RE)
18/05/30     Torre 4-2 Sport Recife
25/05/30     América-PE 5-0 Encruzilhada
25/05/30     Náutico 4-2 Santa Cruz
01/06/30     Náutico 2-3 Íris-PE
01/06/30     Sport Recife 5-3 Flamengo (RE)
01/06/30     Torre 2-1 América-PE
08/06/30     Náutico 4-2 América-PE
22/06/30     Encruzilhada 2-1 Santa Cruz
22/06/30     Sport Recife 5-2 Íris-PE
29/06/30     Flamengo (RE) 3-1 Náutico
29/06/30     Sport Recife 4-2 América-PE
29/06/30     Torre 1-3 Íris-PE
06/07/30     Encruzilhada 0-1 Íris-PE
06/07/30     Flamengo (RE) 2-0 Santa Cruz
13/07/30     Torre 2-0 Flamengo (RE)
20/07/30     Flamengo (RE) 1-2 América-PE
20/07/30     Íris-PE 0-3 Santa Cruz
03/08/30     Sport Recife 2-3 Santa Cruz
10/08/30     Flamengo (RE) 0-1 Encruzilhada
24/08/30     Sport Recife 2-0 Encruzilhada
24/08/30     Torre 3-1 Náutico
31/08/30     Encruzilhada 3-1 Náutico
31/08/30     Flamengo (RE) 3-3 Íris-PE
14/09/30     América-PE 1-0 Íris-PE
14/09/30     Sport Recife 1-2 Torre
                          P   G   W   D   L  GF  GA  GD
 1. Torre                14   9   7   0   2  20  14   6
--------------------------------------------------------
 2. América-PE           11   9   5   1   3  21  15   6
 3. Encruzilhada         10   9   5   0   4  12  15  -3
 4. Náutico               8   9   4   0   5  21  20   1
 5. Sport Recife          8   9   4   0   5  21  20   1
 6. Íris-PE               8  10   3   2   5  17  24  -7
 7. Flamengo (RE)         7   9   3   1   5  15  17  -2
 8. Santa Cruz            6   8   2   2   4  12  14  -2
Obs.: The championship was interrupted due to the Revolução de 1930.
Several matches were not played and the classification above was considered
oficially the final one.
Torre is state champions of 1930.
